hadiths[22]{hadithnumber,text}:
3904,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi kaahin (pujari) ke paas gaya jo ghaib ki khabren deta ho aur phir uski tasdeeq ki, ya apni biwi ke paas uskey ayyame-haiz mein gaya , ya uski peeth mein mubashrat ki to wo Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par nazil karda deen se bari hua.''"
3905,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney nujum (nakshatron) ka koi ilm seekha usney jadu ka eik hissey seekha , chunanche jo is mein apna hissey badhaanaa chahta hai badha ley.''"
3906,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne maqame-Hudebiya mein hamen Fajr ki Namaz padhaai jabke raat ko barish ho chuki thi. Namaz se farigh honey ke baad aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) logon ki taraf mutawajjeh huey aur farmaya : ''kya tumhen maloom hai ke tumharey Rab ne kya kaha hai?'' Sahaba ne kaha : Allah aur uskey Rasool hi khoob jantey hain. aapney farmaya : ''Allah taala ne farmaya hai : merey bandon mein se kuchh mujh par emaan laye hain aur kuchh kafir ho gaey hain. jinhon ne ye kaha ke hamen Allah ke fazal aur uski rehmat se barish mili hai, to wo mujh par emaan laye aur sitarey ke kafir huey hain. aur jinhonne kaha ke hamen falan falan sitarey se barish mili hai, to wo mujh se kafir huey aur sitarey par emaan laye.''"
3907,"Janab Qatan bin Qabisa apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, aap farma rahey they : ''Iyaafa , teer aur turq jadu aur kahaanat mein se hain.'' turq se murad perindey udaanaa aur Iyaafa se murad lakeerein kheenchnaa hai."
3908,Auf (bin Abi Jameela Ea'raab) kehtey hain ke ''Iyaafa'' se murad perindey udaana aur ''turq'' se murad zameen par lakeerein kheenchnaa hai.
3909,Hazrat Muawiya bin Hakam Sulmee (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham mein kuchh log hain jo lakeeren khinchtey hain (un se kuch nataaij nikaltey hain) to aapney farmaya : ''(Allah ke) anbiya mein se eik Nabi lakeeren khincha kartey they. chunanche jiski lakeeren unkey muwaafiq hon wo durust hai.''
3910,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' badshigooni shirk hai, badshigooni shirk hai.'' teen baar farmaya. aur ham mein se her eik ko koi na koi weham ho hi jata hai, magar Shan Wala Allah usey tawakkul ki barkat se zaayel (khatm) kar deta hai."
3911,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi marz mutaaddi (chhoot-wala) nahin na badshigooni hai, na safar ka mahina manhoos hai na murdey ki khopdi mein se koi ullu waghaira nikalta hai.'' eik badwi ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap un oonton ke mutalliq kya kahengey jo registaan mein hirniyon ke manind hotey hain, magar un mein koi khaarish zada oont aa milta hai to sab ko khaarish wala kar deta hai? aapney farmaya : ''bhala pehley ko kis ne bimari lagai thi?'' Maamer ne kaha ke Zohri ne eik aadmi ke wastey se Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kiya ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''kisi bimar ko sehat mand ke sath hergiz na milaao.'' to us aadmi ne Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : kya aapney hamein ye hadees bayan nahin ki hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi bimari mutaaddi (chhoot-wali) nahin hoti, na koi safar ka mahina manhoos hai aur na kisi murdey ki khopdi se ullu nikalta hai.'' to Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya : maine tumhen aisi koi hadees bayan nahin ki. Zohri ne kaha ke Abu-Salma ne kaha : hadees to unhoney bayan ki thi aur maine nahin suna ke Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ko is hadees ke siwa kabhi koi hadees bhooli ho."
3912,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' koi bimari mutaaddi (chhoot-wali) nahin hoti , na kisi murdey se koi ullu nikalta hai, na kisi sitarey ki koi taaseer hai aur na safar ka mahina manhoos hai.''"
3913,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi jin bhoot nahin (ke jangalon mein mukhtalif shaklon se logon ko raah se bhatkaaye.'')
3914,"Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke meri maujudgi mein Haris bin Miskeen ke samney hadees padhi gaee, Ash'hab ne tumhen bataya ke Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) se (koi safar nahi) ka mafhoom puchha gaya to unhoney kaha : daure-jahiliyat mein log maah safar ko eik saal halal qarar dey letey they aur eik saal haram, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''safar mein tabdeeli sahih nahin.''"
3915,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi marz mutaadd (chhoot-wala) nahin hota aur na koi bad-shagooni hai, albatta nek-shagoonii mujhey bhali lagti hai. nek-shagooni (ki eik soorat ye hai ke) aadmi koi achcha kalima sun ley.''"
3916,"Muhammad bin Rashid ne (Haam) ki wazahat mein kaha : ehale jahiliyat samajhtey they ke murda jab dafn kiya jata hai to uski qabr se eik ullu nikalta hai. safar ke mutalliq puchha to kaha : ehale-jahiliyat (is mahine) safar ko manhoos samajhtey they, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne iski mana farma di. Muhammad bin Rashid ne kaha : ham ne kaee logon se suna hai ke us se murad ''pet ka dard'' hai aur wo usey mutaaddi (chhoot-wala) samajhtey they to farmaya gaya ke ''koi safar nahin.''"
3917,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne koi kalma suna jo aap ko pasand aaya to aapney farmaya : ''ham ne tumhari faal tumharey munh (ke alfaz) se li hai.''
3918,"Janab Ata (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kya ke log kehtey hain : ''safar se murad pet ka dard hai.'' Juraij ne poochh ke ''haama'' kya hai? to kaha ke log samajhtey hain ye parinda insani rooh hota hai jo cheekhta chalata rehta hai. halanke, insani rooh nahin hota balke koi zamini janwer hai."
3919,"Janab Urwa bin Aamir, Ahmed qarshi se riwayat kartey ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki majlis mein) taira ( '' بدفالی '' ka zikr hua to aapney farmaya : '' un mein behtar nek shaguni hai aur ye (bad faali ke auhaam) kisi musalman ko) apney kaam sey) mat roken , agar koi shakhs koi naa-pasandida chiz dekhey to chahiye ke yun kahey (اللهم ! لا يأتي بالحسنات إلا أنت ، ولا يدفع السيئات إلا أنت ، ولا حول ولا قوة إلا بك) ''aey Allah ! terey siwa koi kisi tarah ki koi bhalai nahin la sakta aur terey siwa koi kisi burai ko rok nahin sakta , burai ka door hona aur bhalai ka hasil hona teri madad hi se mumkin hai.''"
3920,"Janab Abdullah bin Barida apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kabhi kisi cheez se badshaguni nahin liya kartey they. aap jab kisi shakhs ko aamil bana kar bhejtey to uska naam daryaft farmatey . so agar uska naam pasand aa jata to khush hotey aur khushi ka asar chehrey par zahir hota aur agar naam pasand na aata to uska asar bhi aap ke chehrey par zahir hota . aur aap jab kisi ( naee ( basti mein dakhil hotey to uska naam poochhtey , agar uska naam pasand aata to khush hotey aur khushi ka asar chehrey par dikhai deta aur naam pasand na aata to uski karaahat ka asar ( bhi) aap ke chehrey par zahir hota ."
3921,"Hazrat Saad bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : '' kisi murdey se koi ullu nahin nikalta , na koi marz mutaddi hota hai aur na badshigooni hai, agar ho bhi to ghodey , aurat aur ghar mein ho sakti hai.''"
3922,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' badshaguni ghar , biwi aur ghodey mein hoti hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Janab Haris bin miskeen ke samney hadees padhi gaee jabkey main hazir tha, unhen kaha gaya ke aap ko ibn Qasim ne khabar di , jabkey Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) se ghodey aur ghar ki badshaguni ke baarey mein puchha gaya? to unhoney farmaya : kitney hi gharon mein logon ne rihaaish ikhtiyar ki to wo halak ho gaey, phir doosrey qiyam pazeer huey to wo bhi halak ho gaey . yehi uski tauzeeh hai jaisey ke ham samajhtey hain. aur Allah khoob janta hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne riwayat kya ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : ghar ki chatai us aurat se kahin behtar hai jo baanjh ho."
3923,"Janab farwa bin Museik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! hamarey yahan eik zameen hai jisey ( أبين ( kaha jata hai. us mein hamarey khet hain aur ye hamarey ghalla uganey ki jagah hai, magar waba wali hai, ya kaha ke badi sakht waba wali jagah hai. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey chhod do . waba wali jagah mein rehney se aadmi halak ho jata hai.''"
3924,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke eik shakhs ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham eik ghar mein they, us mein ham bahut se afrad they aur wahan hamarey amwaal bhi bahut they. phir ham eik doosrey ghar mein muntaqil huey to hamarey afrad kam ho gaey aur amwaal mein bhi qillat ho gaee. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''usey chhod do , ye bura ghar hai.''"
3925,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik juzami ka haath pakda aur apney sath khaney ke piyaley mein dal diya aur farmaya : ''Allah par aitimaad aur tawakkul kartey huey khao .'' ( ham bhi tumharey sath khatey hain. (
